message: There's been a lot of administrative changes in HTPS this year: Mrs. Fisher, who was the HHS principal for 1 year, moved to Amsterdam and is now the principal there after Dr. Mullady retired. Mr. DiLollo was hired to replace Fisher as the HHS principal. Dr. Jenkins is back at Sunnymead after Dr. Jablonski, 1 of the HHS VP's, filled in at Woods Road and Sunnymead for parts of last year. Dr. Fishbein is now the interim superintendent. Mr. Volpe will be the new superintendent starting in February.
